             was again indicted for <rs id="t18270913-354-off1965" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270913-354-off1965" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-354-off1965" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270913-354-cd1966" type="crimeDate">17th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-354-off1965 t18270913-354-cd1966"></join>, 1 table spoon, value 10s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18270913-354-victim2566" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Mariner
               <interp inst="t18270913-354-victim2566" type="surname" value="Mariner"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-354-victim2566" type="given" value="William"></interp>
